about.summary: A validation library for Pandas data frames using user-friendly schemas

name: pandas_schema
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pandas_schema" %}
{% set version = "0.3.5" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: e68e93862cf728d2c4cec5237cf62e410d19be168c1c6d68fa5ed13bf543c6d6

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python  >3
  run:
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - python  >3

test:
  imports:
    - pandas_schema

about:
  home: "https://github.com/TMiguelT/PandasSchema"
  license: GPL3
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "A validation library for Pandas data frames using user-friendly schemas"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - foellmelanie
